            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Quick update on this:\n\nSo it seems like the reason for this is because of this constant:\n\nhttps://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/9c9c7ae30f50685e62984084767905c7d456cdd9/src/nvim/drawline.h#L12\n\nWe limit the max terminal highlight attributes to 1024, but the UI compositor doesn't account for this here:\n\nhttps://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/3b54adc6c6d25dd146fa1eac21321f6bd612f50a/src/nvim/ui_compositor.c#L546\n\nAs well as in a few other locations. I'm currently trying to figure out how I can make sure that we don't go past this index in the ScreenGrid's highlight attributes in terminals.",
